#: ../../apm/apm-alert-visualize/alert-conditions-apm.rst:42
msgid "Alerts when latency anomalously spikes compared to the same periods in the past (for cyclical or seasonal data). Anomaly can be defined through number of deviations from historical norm or percentage change compared to historical norm."
