#: ../../apm/db-query-perf/db-query-performance.rst:71
msgid ":strong:`Isolate database issues:` Determine whether an increase in the latency or error rate of a service is related to problems with a database. If it is, you can quickly identify which database and which specific query is contributing the most latency, so you can resolve it by involving the DBA or the owner of the service that's making the slow database call."
