#: ../../apm/span-tags/index-tag-tips.rst:114
msgid "For example, consider two services, ``frontend`` and ``checkoutservice``. Each service exists in two regions. The ``frontend`` service has five endpoints, and the ``checkoutservice`` has two endpoints. ``region`` and ``endpoint`` are indexed tags for each service. There are no other indexed tags in this scenario."
